eacute;tat d\'esprit : le partage et l\'&eacute;change. 3 jours de pur plaisir Ce qui est g&eacute;nial, c\'est la passion et l\'engouement que peuvent avoir l\'ensemble des participants et conf&eacute;renciers. Le Road Trip incluait une sacr&eacute; DreamTeam de Fran&ccedil;ais pr&ecirc;ts &agrave; en d&eacute;coudre avec WP. Contrairement aux autres &eacute;v&egrave;nements auxquels j\'ai d&eacute;j&agrave; particip&eacute; sur le e-marketing ou le SEO, l\'&eacute;tat d\'esprit est plus ouvert [&hellip;]</p>\n<hr>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/seomix-wordpress/~4/DGTD_iU7JZw\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\">\n</div>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:50:\"WP Formation : Créer un e-Commerce avec WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:2:\"id\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:50:\"http://wpformation.com/creer-e-commerce-wordpress/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:2:{s:3:\"rel\";s:9:\"alternate\";s:4:\"href\";s:50:\"http://wpformation.com/creer-e-commerce-wordpress/\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:9:\"published\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"2013-10-15T07:00:35+00:00\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:6:\"author\";a:1:{i:0;a: